        "• $\\tanh(x) = \\frac{e^x - e^{-x}}{e^x + e^{-x}} = 2\\sigma(2x) - 1 \\in (-1, 1)$ — zero-centered",
        "• Leaky ReLU: $\\max(\\alpha x, x)$, $\\alpha \\approx 0.01$",
        "• PReLU: $\\max(\\alpha x, x)$, $\\alpha$ learned",
        "• ELU: $x$ if $x > 0$ else $\\alpha(e^x - 1)$",
        "• GELU: $x \\cdot \\Phi(x) \\approx 0.5x(1 + \\tanh(\\sqrt{2/\\pi}(x + 0.044715x^3)))$",
