        "• Softmax: $\\sigma(z_i) = \\frac{e^{z_i}}{\\sum_j e^{z_j}}$",
        "• Softplus: $\\ln(1 + e^x)$ — smooth ReLU",
        "• Dead ReLU: neuron outputs 0 for all inputs (irrecoverable)",
